title: S4, Ep5: Lowkey Movin' On

itunes:summary:
The big day is finally here — it’s Block Party time! Crissle and Fran get into music fest etiquette, parenting goals and discuss the likelihood of one of the wildest fan theories we’ve heard so far coming true.

Don’t forget to join in on the conversation and follow along on social media with the hashtag #insecuriTEA
